{"word":"G1573 - ἐκκακέω - ekkakéō - ek-kak-eh'-o - Faint","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκκακέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekkakéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-kak-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Faint</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சோர்ந்துபோ"},{"paragraph":"to be utterly spiritless, to be wearied out, exhausted"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G2556 - κακός - kakós - kak-os'/2556\">G2556</a>; to <i>be</i> (<i>bad</i> or) <i>weak</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>fail</i> (in heart): - faint, be weary.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1573/1573\">G1573</a>, <a href=\"#/G172/172\">G172</a>, <a href=\"#/G2549/2549\">G2549</a>, <a href=\"#/G2550/2550\">G2550</a>, <a href=\"#/G2554/2554\">G2554</a>, <a href=\"#/G2555/2555\">G2555</a>, <a href=\"#/G2556/2556\">G2556</a>, <a href=\"#/G2557/2557\">G2557</a>, <a href=\"#/G420/420\">G420</a>"}]}